content:
Renew Policy Business Process

When it's time to renew your policy, you get an email with a renewal link. Then all you have to do is enter some details for the renewal and it's all done.

The Renew Policy OmniScript is available in OmniScripts under:

Type - insFSC/RenewPolicy
Version Name - Renew Policy FSC

You can launch this OmniScript from:
- Broker Portal (Broker or Agent)
- Customer Portal (Customer who owns insurance policies)
- Vlocity Admin Lightning Experience (Internal insurance agent, Vlocity admin)

Here's a look at the workflow to renew your policy:

The OmniScript takes a policy Id and uses services to retrieve data about the vehicles insured by this policy and the corresponding coverages for them. It then displays the vehicle and coverage details, lets users modify coverages, and updates the price accordingly.

Next, it creates a renewed policy using an integration procedure. A Data Mapper then updates the old policy record renewal information.

There are three ways to renew policies:
- Renew a Policy from the Policy UI
- Renew Policies from the Digital Experience Site
- Renew a Policy Through Email
title: Renewing Insurance Policies with Salesforce
